2006-07-25  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Includes.

	* doc/manual/developer.tex (Includes): New.

2006-07-24  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* data/vaucanson.el: Use `file-name-nondirectory' on
	non-include/vaucanson files.

2006-07-24  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* data/vaucanson.el: Fix use of `c-header-file-extensions'.

2006-07-24  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* data/misc.el: Move...
	* data/vaucanson.el: Here.  Add `cpp-check-guard' that checks the CPP
	guard for a standard #ifndef/#define/#endif scheme.  Use it in
	M-x vaucansonize-buffer RET.  Provide `vaucanson' package.
	* data/Makefile.am: Update accordingly.

2006-07-24  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* include/vaucanson/misc/unique.hcc: Remove.  `unique.hxx' is the name.
	* src/vaucanswig/meta/vauto.cc: Remove useless `include' in comment.

2006-07-24  Robert Bigaignon  <robert.bigaignon@lrde.epita.fr>

	Change namespace in krat_exp_linearize_structure test.

	This patch helps Vaucanson to pass make check.
	see http://vaucanson.lrde.org/trac.cgi/ticket/74

	* src/tests/algebra/series/krat/main/krat_exp_linearize_structure_test.hh:
	Change << operator namespace.

2006-07-24  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Separate common commands for all types from commands specific to automata.

	* taf-kit/src/common_automaton_commands.hh: New. Add commands specific
	to automata only.
	* taf-kit/src/b_commands.cc,
	* taf-kit/src/common_commands.hh,
	* taf-kit/src/Makefile.am,
	* taf-kit/src/z_commands.cc: Update accordingly.

2006-07-24  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Add sub_normalize_here.

	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/sub_normalize.hh: Add two algorithms
	 list in reference documentation..
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/sub_normalize.hxx: Add in-place version
	of sub_normalize.
	* taf-kit/src/tdc_commands.cc,
	* taf-kit/src/getters.hxx: Use it.

2006-07-24  Florent Terrones  <terron_f@lrde.epita.fr>

	* src/tests/xml/tester.sh: Correct some directory names so as to work in
	another directory than srcdir. Closes ticket #81.

2006-07-24  Guillaume Leroi  <guillaume.leroi@lrde.epita.fr>

	Fix some typos.

	* taf-kit/src/tdc_commands.cc: Add dots at end of lines.
	Cut long strings in two.
	* taf-kit/src/edition_commands.hxx: Reindent macros.

