2006-07-19  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	Permit functors to return Booleans used as a loop stopper.

	* include/vaucanson/misc/static.hh: Declare static Booleans type
	`true_t' and `false_t'. Declare a macro to convert Booleans to static
	Booleans.
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/graph.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/automata/implementation/graph.hxx: Factor. Define
	different `deltaf'. Dispatch according to the return type of the
	functor. If it's Bool, then stop the loop if the functor returns
	false on an input.
	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/automata_base.hh: Document.

2006-07-18  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* include/vaucanson/tools/usual_macros.hh: Pacify check_xml.sh.

2006-07-17  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	Autoconf 2.60.

	* configure.ac: Require Autoconf 2.60, which fixes issues such as
	forbidden/allowed tokens.
	* build-aux/vcsn-xml.m4, build-aux/vcsn.m4: Likewise.
	* build-aux: Do not ignore files such as ltversion.m4 that should
	not exist.  We use Libtool 1.5.*, not 2.* that does seem to have
	problems with Autoconf 2.60.
	* src/vaucanswig/expand.sh (output, canonical): New, use them.
	I have a file using `-' instead of `_', and that broke the
	generation of Makefile.ams.

2006-07-11  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* include/vaucanson/automata/concept/automata_ops.hxx: Don't give a
	name to the structure.
	* src/benchs/generate_benchs.sh: Output `<<', not `\<\<'.

2006-07-08  Michaël Cadilhac  <michael.cadilhac@lrde.epita.fr>

	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/eval.hh,
	* include/vaucanson/algorithms/eval.hxx: Use `deltaf', remove the
	Boolean flag of `eval'.
	* src/tests/automata/algos/letter_combination_labeled_graphs/product_test.hh:
	Remove the use of Boolean flag of `eval'. THIS TEST IS NOW BROKEN,
	in particular for z_automata.

